title: Episode 184: DeFi, NFTs & Current Crypto Trends Explained…
description:
Show Notes:
Robbie’s take on the Tensions between Russia and Ukraine and how most American’s living in Ukraine are handling the threat of war… [00:10]
Cool travel spots in Turkey… [02:50]
Robbie’s lucky 6 figure payoff in crypto story… [05:00]
The link between early crypto investing and gaming… [07:30]
How often do you hear the rags to riches crypto stories from Millennials hitting it big with bitcoin? [12:30]
The “Never Sell” culture and how some are opting-out of fiat currency… [13:22]
How to compare crypto to social media to wrap your head around the value of crypto… [14:45]
Will crypto companies replace and disrupt the banking industry? [16:20]
WTF is DeFi? [16:53]
How decentralized finance works and why it’s a game changer for the loan industry…. [17:45]
How you can make money passively loaning out your bitcoin… [19:30]
Why crypto is so confusing, even to experts… [21:20]
What sort of crypto assets should newbs invest in? [22:30]
“Pristine Collateral” – The Real Estate of The Crypto Space… [23:30]
The heartbreaking story about Gun’s Crypto Fund and how you can lose your ass using leverage if you’re not careful… [24:00]
What were the “Fork Wars” of 2016 and 2017? [25:30]
Why ore Bitcoin transactions so slow? [25:50]
What is trading on margin? [27:35]
What is “Max Pain” and how you can get liquidated… [29:00]
Bitcoins year over year percentage return… [31:45]
WTF is a NFT? [32:10]
Why are NFTs valuable and what are their application? [32:50]
Music rights as an example of a NFT use case… [34:00]
Why NFTs are useful for the collectibles industry… [37:53]
How “smart money” is investing in NFTs… [40:00]
Comparing NFTs to Napster… [44:00]
How blockchain technology can disrupt Uber… [45:45]
How you could short the stocks of traditional media companies and potentially make a killing… [47:00]
What does non-fungable token mean and how to research NFTs on Open Sea… [48:32]
Aaron’s Alt Coin picks… [50:47]
What does the “Market Capitalization Rate” mean and how to use it to understand the value of meme coins… [52:35]
When should you think about putting your crypto holdings to work to create passive income? [55:35]
What is a yield farm? [56:53]
How you can take stable-coin loans from your crypto assets and why the yields are higher than in other asset classes… [58:14]
What are the risks associated with DeFi investing… [59:40]
What is a liquidity pool? [01:01:07]
How to “print money” using crypto farming… [01:03:57]
Do we know who the creator of Bitcoin, Satoshi Nakamoto, is? [01:09:21]
How much Bitcoin is lost forever? What if you lose your bitcoin in a “boating accident”… [01:11:11]
Metrics for understanding when to sell your crypto positions… [01:15:02]
How to “scale out” and sell your position to get the best returns on your investment… [01:17:40]

I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
